(* The first component of pairs, which infsum is over, can be discarded. *)
(* The basic observation is that 
    A = {(s::'a, v\<^sub>0::'a) | s v\<^sub>0. put\<^bsub>x\<^esub> v\<^sub>0 (e v\<^sub>0) = s}
is resulted from an injective function 
